        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-44" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#647687;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#314354;" value="&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;Bu arayüz, sadece bir veri görüntüleme paneli değil; backend tarafında &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;71&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;71&quot;&gt;core_scrapper&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/b&gt; ve &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;88&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;88&quot;&gt;ai_advisor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/b&gt; modülleri tarafından işlenen ham verinin, lojistik ve ticari içgörüye dönüştürüldüğü bir &quot;Akıllı Kontrol Noktası&quot;dır.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Bu Dashboard Ne Yapar?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Veri Görselleştirme:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;21&quot;&gt;Amazon UK/Global&lt;/code&gt; kaynaklarından otonom olarak çekilen; fiyat, stok, puan ve rekabet verilerini &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;116&quot;&gt;React&lt;/code&gt; ve &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;125&quot;&gt;Lucide-React&lt;/code&gt; bileşenleri ile dinamik grafiklere dönüştürür.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;AI Tabanlı Analitik:&lt;/b&gt; Dashboard üzerindeki her bir ürün kartı, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;62&quot;&gt;Gemini 1.5 Flash&lt;/code&gt; modelimiz tarafından analiz edilmiş; kârlılık potansiyeli ve piyasa riskine göre filtrelenmiştir.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Anlık Karar Desteği:&lt;/b&gt; Kullanıcıya, ürün bazlı trend tahminlerini ve rakip analizlerini görsel bir özetle sunarak, ticaret süreçlerinde &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;134&quot;&gt;&quot;tahmine dayalı değil, veriye dayalı&quot;&lt;/b&gt; hızlı aksiyon almasını sağlar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="820" width="510" x="3880" y="264.03" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-50" edge="1" parent="1" source="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-48" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-44" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-48" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#647687;strokeColor=#314354;fontColor=#ffffff;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Nasıl Çalışır?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Veri Entegrasyonu:&lt;/b&gt; Frontend, backend&#39;deki &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;42&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;FastAPI&lt;/code&gt; endpoint&#39;lerini kullanarak SQLite veritabanından işlenmiş veriyi &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;115&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;JSON&lt;/code&gt; formatında çeker.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Modüler Mimari:&lt;/b&gt; Bileşen bazlı (component-based) tasarımı sayesinde; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;68&quot;&gt;Sustainability&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;84&quot;&gt;Demand Pool&lt;/code&gt; veya &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;101&quot;&gt;Gümrük Mevzuat&lt;/code&gt; gibi modüller dashboard&#39;a entegre edilmiştir. Bu yapı, sisteme yeni lojistik modüllerin hızla eklenmesine olanak tanır.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Güvenlik ve Performans:&lt;/b&gt; API haberleşmesi &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;41&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;TypeScript&lt;/code&gt; tip güvenliği ile optimize edilmiş, hassas yapılandırmalar &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;7,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;111&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; yönetimiyle izole edilmiştir.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="661.83" width="470" x="4500" y="343.11" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-51" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="205" width="353.45" x="4083.27" y="-1785.97" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-55" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="213.06" width="368.41" x="4490" y="-1790" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-57" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#647687;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#314354;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;🚛 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;LogisticsPage: Otonom Navlun ve Rota Optimizasyon Modülü&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Ne Yapar? (Fonksiyon)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;Bu modül, e-ticaret lojistik süreçlerinin en karmaşık kısmı olan &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;65&quot;&gt;navlun maliyeti hesaplama ve rota verimliliği analizini&lt;/b&gt; üstlenir. Kullanıcıdan alınan ürün verilerini (ağırlık, boyut, varış noktası) işleyerek; kargo maliyetlerini, gümrük vergisi tahminlerini ve lojistik riskleri saniyeler içinde hesaplar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Nasıl Yapar? (İşleyiş)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;Kullanıcı arayüzünde girdiği parametreleri, bir &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;48&quot;&gt;LojistikFormu.tsx&lt;/code&gt; bileşeni ile toplar. Bu veriler &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;98&quot;&gt;Axios&lt;/code&gt; üzerinden backend&#39;deki &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;127&quot;&gt;FastAPI&lt;/code&gt; endpoint&#39;ine (&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;149&quot;&gt;/api/logistics&lt;/code&gt;) gönderilir. Backend, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;186&quot;&gt;ai_advisor&lt;/code&gt; (Gemini 1.5 Flash) modülümüzü kullanarak mevcut piyasadaki lojistik eğilimlerini analiz eder ve kullanıcıya &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;305&quot;&gt;&quot;Maliyet Etkin Rota&quot;&lt;/b&gt; önerisi sunar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Neyle Yapar? (Teknoloji)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Frontend:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;React&lt;/code&gt; ve &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;19&quot;&gt;Vite&lt;/code&gt; tabanlı dinamik form yönetimi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Backend:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;Python&lt;/code&gt; tabanlı mantık motoru ve &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;41&quot;&gt;FastAPI&lt;/code&gt; (RESTful API).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Zeka:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;Gemini 1.5 Flash&lt;/code&gt; ile dinamik maliyet analizi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Görselleştirme:&lt;/b&gt; Hesaplanan maliyet dağılımını &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;46&quot;&gt;Chart.js&lt;/code&gt; veya özel &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;65&quot;&gt;React&lt;/code&gt; grafik kütüphaneleriyle &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;95&quot;&gt;pasta grafiği (pie chart)&lt;/b&gt; olarak kullanıcıya sunar.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="585" width="360" x="4550" y="-1486.47" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-66" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="361.03" x="5210" y="-1154.97" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="PL-6ytz9YCu_dIU6WfZg-68" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#647687;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#314354;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;⚖️ &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;CustomsPage: Gümrük Mevzuat ve GTIP Kütüphanesi&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.04px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ne Yapar? (Fonksiyon)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;Bu modül, uluslararası ticaretteki en büyük bariyer olan &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;57&quot;&gt;gümrükleme süreçlerini dijitalleştirir.&lt;/b&gt; Kullanıcının arattığı ürünün GTIP (Gümrük Tarife İstatistik Pozisyonu) kodunu tanımlar, ilgili ülkenin vergi oranlarını (KDV, Gümrük Vergisi vb.) hesaplar ve ürünün ithalat/ihracat yasaklarına takılıp takılmayacağını denetler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;10&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;2. Nasıl Yapar? (İşleyiş)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot;&gt;Kullanıcı &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;CustomsPage&lt;/code&gt; üzerinde ürün adını veya GTIP kodunu girer. Frontend, bu veriyi backend&#39;deki &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;99&quot;&gt;FastAPI&lt;/code&gt; gümrük servisimize gönderir. Backend, &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;145&quot;&gt;ai_advisor&lt;/code&gt; modülümüzü kullanarak ilgili gümrük mevzuatını yorumlar; eğer ürün bir kısıtlamaya tabiyse (örneğin &quot;elektronik kısıtlaması&quot;) kullanıcıyı anında uyarır.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4 data-path-to-node=&quot;12&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;12&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;3. Neyle Yapar? (Teknoloji)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;13&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;13,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Frontend:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;13,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;React&lt;/code&gt; arayüzü ile hızlı arama ve tablo tabanlı vergi gösterimi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;13,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Backend:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;13,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;Python&lt;/code&gt; ile mevzuat veri setlerini işleme ve &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;13,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;53&quot;&gt;FastAPI&lt;/code&gt; ile güvenli API bağlantısı.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Zeka:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;13,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;Gemini API&lt;/code&gt; ile karmaşık mevzuat metinlerinin &quot;ticari karar&quot; diline çevrilmesi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;13,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;13,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Veri Yönetimi:&lt;/b&gt; Güncel GTIP veritabanı (backend üzerinde optimize edilmiş sorgular).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="630" width="450" x="5701.01" y="-934.97" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
